title: 125: Reggie Wayne weighs in on new look offenses, college football talk and more
itunes:title: 125: Reggie Wayne weighs in on new look offenses, college football talk and more
description:
NFL Network's Reggie Wayne joins former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks to discuss what makes the league's current stars special and how offenses have changed. The trio also provide insight on the action from Week 5 and look ahead to the upcoming slate of college match-ups.
